<HEADLINE>
<P>
LASER MEDICAL CHANGES NAME TO BIOLASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Laser Medical Technology Inc. said it has changed its name to Biolase 
Technology Inc. 
</P>
<P>
 The new name will take effect Monday. At the same time, the company will be 
identified on the Nasdaq market, where its common stock is traded, by its new 
symbol, BLTI. 
</P>
<P>
 The company, based in San Clemente, makes and markets laser products and 
specialized materials for the dental and medical markets. 
</P>
