Freeway connector** $39.0 1992 3. California 118 from the Santa Paula Freeway 
to Vineyard Avenue*** $22.1 1992 4. Ventura Freeway from Vineyard Avenue to 
Johnson Drive $57.6 1996 5. Ventura Freeway at Seaward Avenue $9.0 1997 6. 
